  Locus:
    Page: 247
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Here & Now
---
No matter what looms ahead, you can eat today, enjoy the sunlight today,
mix good cheer with friends today; enjoy it and bless God for it. Do not
look back on happiness -- dream of it in the future.
